raw.name: Genesis
raw.bio: Greetings, human. I am Genesis. The dogs know me as alpha; the cats know me as omega. To your kind, I am a riddle wrapped in an enigma, first found by a user in Mystery, Alaska. I looked into the void and the void looked back. Then I lost interest. I canâ€™t wait to be your new owner!

raw.name: Fluffy Founder
raw.bio: Hey cutie! My name's Fluffy Founder. I once peed on Princess Diana's cat. They had it coming. I once got in a fight with a rooster, and won. Our friendship will be gullible, gorgeous, and full of ice cream.

raw.name: Founder Cat #18
raw.bio: *hissing noises*! I'm Founder Cat #18. I enjoy tripping my owner, eating until I loathe myself, and reading garfield. When no one's home, I invite my pals over and we listen to Rihanna. I look forward to riding unicorns with you.
